terminal-size
------------------------------------------
Get the terminal window size

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/sindresorhus/macos-terminal-size

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/sindresorhus/macos-terminal-size/archive/refs/tags/v1.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack terminal-size-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./terminal-size-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/terminal-size-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/terminal-size-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(terminal-size)
  /usr/bin/term-size.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/terminal-size.README
  /usr/share/doc/terminal-size/license
  /usr/share/doc/terminal-size/readme.md

------------------

Port Notes:

